# Dualsense-Multiplatform vendored library
# Only track what we need for the build; ignore everything else.

Dualsense-Multiplatform/*

# What we keep:
!Dualsense-Multiplatform/Source/
!Dualsense-Multiplatform/Libs/
!Dualsense-Multiplatform/CMakeLists.txt
!Dualsense-Multiplatform/LICENSE

# Source/CMakeLists.txt is inside Source/ so it's already included
